data.description: Are You Looking For Horse Property in Cottonwood? This 12.81 Acre Property in Quail Ridge Ranches is For YOU! This Renovated 3 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom Home Has a Split Floor Plan with an Oversized Primary Bedroom with En Suite, Two Additional Spacious Bedrooms, a Bathroom and an Indoor Laundry Room.  The Kitchen Has Ample Counter and Cabinet Space, Stainless Steel Appliances and Beautiful LVP Flooring. The Fenced Backyard is the Perfect Place For Kids, Pets, BBQs and Spending Time with Family. There is Ample Room For Horses and Riding Trails Galore! The 2 Car Carport and NEW Storage Shed Are Included! If You Are Looking For Peace and Quite, Room to Roam, Space For Animals and Gardening, This is the Property For You!
